## Dataset License

The IBM HR Analytics Employee Attrition & Performance dataset used in this project
is licensed under the Database Contents License (DbCL v1.0).

**Dataset Source:** IBM HR Analytics Employee Attrition & Performance  
**Dataset URL:** https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/pavansubhasht/ibm-hr-analytics-attrition-dataset  
**License:** DbCL (Database Contents License) v1.0  
**License URL:** http://opendatacommons.org/licenses/dbcl/1.0/  
**Creator:** IBM Data Scientists (Fictional dataset)  
**Published by:** pavansubhash on Kaggle

### About the Dataset

This is a fictional data set created by IBM data scientists to explore factors
that lead to employee attrition. The dataset contains various employee attributes
including demographics, job-related factors, compensation, and work-life factors.

